  "title": "CLASS 4 DRIVER",
  "description": "<ul><li>Loading and unloading of uniforms/linens trolley at factory & customer premises</li><li>Ensure correct loading of goods onto delivery vehicles</li><li>Ensure timely delivery of goods to customers</li><li>Document handling such as D/O and Invoice</li><li>Provide good customer service during delivery</li><li>Adhere to assigned routes & follow time schedules</li><li>Abide by all transportation laws & maintain safe driving records</li><li>Handle vehicles, equipment & devices provided by company with care</li><li>Maintain basic housekeeping, cleanliness & hygiene of vehicle assigned</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties assigned by supervisor/manager</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Class 3 & 4 driving License</li><li>Good attitude & willing to learn</li><li>Good communication skills</li><li>Able to commit to 6 day work week schedule with rotational off days</li><li>Have basic knowledge in maintenance of vehicle</li></ul>",
